Accendero Web App
This is a simple web app that collects user data and also allow you to edit and delete a user.

Initial Setup:
Decided on what editor to use.
Decided on what language to use.
Decided on what where to store data.
Create a repo for the project.


In this project, I used VS code editor.
Language: TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS
Database: MongoDB
Repo: https://github.com/manniestien/AccenderoProject




Learning Sources: https://angular.io/
                  https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/forms/overview/
                  https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8945751/html-form-submit


